openapi: 3.0.1
info:

servers:
- description: SwaggerHub API Auto Mocking

      summary: InCR Initiate a fraud case
      description: InCR Initiate a fraud case
      operationId: Initiate
      parameters: []
      requestBody:
        $ref: '#/components/requestBodies/FraudResolutionProcedure'
